Brief Description: Full-text electronic archive of selected volumes of American poetry prior to 1920.
Description: <p>This collection contains full-text electronic archive of selected volumes of American poetry prior to 1920. Most of the archive is made up of 19th century poetry, although a few 18th century and early 20th century texts are included.</p>
